Summer Game Jam 2011
Theme:	Twice Upon a Time
Game:	Little Red Riding Wolves
	First you must build an army of wolves to thwart the AI Red.
	After your minions have destroyed her then you must avoid that same army in order to reach the house yourself.
	Are you smarter than Mecha Red Riding Hood?


Dependencies:
cmake
freeglut3-dev
libxmu-dev
libxi-dev
libpng12-dev
zlib1g-dev

(Windows)
http://gnuwin32.sourceforge.net/packages/zlib.htm
http://gnuwin32.sourceforge.net/packages/libpng.htm
http://www.xmission.com/~nate/glut/glut-3.7.6-bin.zip


Build with:
cmake /path/to/checkout
make

Run:
/path/to/checkout/wolves

Ubuntu Convenience Command from within the checkout directory:
sudo apt-get install cmake freeglut3-dev libxmu-dev libxi-dev libpng12-dev zlib1g-dev && cmake . && make && ./wolves



Controls and Mechanics:

The Game is split into 3 phases.

Place Wolf phase:
	Place wolves with left click
	Space to end phase

AI Red phase:
	Mecha Red tries to reach house without being consumed
	You lose if Red achieves sanctuary in the house
	Phase ends when Red is eaten

Player Red phase:
	Red chases your mouse
	If you guide her safely around wolves and trees to grandma's house, you win!
